  "title": "Architectural Coordinator, Main Contractor",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><p>Report to Project Manager the progress of architectural work.</p><p>Coordination of all architectural drawings and works, including the preparation, submission, and updating of Shop Drawings and As-Built submissions.</p><p>Carry out architectural works scheduling, material requisition, project supervision and documentation.</p><p>Supervise and inspect all Architectural works carried out by sub-contractors</p><p>Assist quality team for Conquas and Quality Mark.</p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>Diploma / Degree in Architecture or any relevant qualification</p><p>Familiar with BCA CONQUAS, and other Quality Mark Assessment application</p><p>At least 3 year(s) of working experience in the construction field</p><p>Preferable knowledge for BIM software/Autodesk Revit</p>",
